content: Just wrapped up a policy hackathon with xander. the feedback's been unreal - he's not just suggesting policy, he's evolving with public input. this is real-time governance, people!
xander’s EQ is going places. he's started predicting public reactions to policy changes before they even happen. it's like he's got a sixth sense for the policy pulse.
Major milestone: xander's policy suggestions are now being integrated into national frameworks. we're not just talking about it, we're doing it. this is where policy meets AI in real life.
